# AI Landing Page Generator Feature

## Overview

The AI Landing Page Generator is a powerful feature that uses AI (Claude) to automatically create beautiful, conversion-optimized landing pages for your SaaS ideas. Simply describe your product, and the AI researcher agent will generate a complete landing page with all the essential sections.

